Gold Price in Hong Kong Down 
The gold price in Hong Kong fell 17 HK dollars to close at 2,832 HK
dollars a tael Thursday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major
gold dealers in Hong Kong.
The gold price is equivalent to 306.78 U.S. dollars a troy ounce, down
1.84 U.S. dollars from the previous close at Thursday's exchange rate
of one U.S. dollar to 7.7490 HK dollars.
